<DOC><DOCNO> WSJ880916-0171 </DOCNO><HL> Stifel Financial to Buy Firm </HL><SO> </SO><CO> SF </CO><IN> TNM </IN><DATELINE> ST. LOUIS  </DATELINE><TEXT>   Stifel Financial Corp. said it agreed to acquire Rowland, Simon andamp; Co. Both are brokerage concerns based here. Terms weren't disclosed.    Stifel said the transaction, which is subject to approval by the boards of both companies, is expected to be completed by the end of the year. </TEXT></DOC>